reviewText: Arrived quickly and exactly as advertised.  Thank you!

Unfortunately this VHS album contains only 3 Videos. It is worth owning because this VHS has the ONLY MOVIE version to New Moon On Monday. At least that I am aware of. I am a TRUE Duran Duran die hard, and unless a new piece or set of Duran Duran material has come out...the only MOVIE VERSION to New Moon On Monday is on this VHS. Hope this review helps. Peace.
